<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>VoxYZ奶油风格主页</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1 class="title">VoxYZ 奶油手绘风</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">统一背景色为标准奶油色 #faf8f3</p>
        </header>
        
        <main>
            <section class="card">
                <h2>设计理念</h2>
                <p>采用浅奶油色背景，搭配手绘风格元素，营造温馨舒适的视觉体验。</p>
            </section>
            
            <section class="card">
                <h2>特色元素</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>手绘虚线边框</li>
                    <li>点阵网格背景</li>
                    <li>不规则圆角设计</li>
                    <li>黄色高亮笔效果</li>
                </ul>
            </section>
        </main>
    </div>
</body>
</html>